fields.calculatedFormula:
IF(ISBLANK(smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c), "Unknown",
  IF (AND( smartystreets__Address_Daylight_Savings__c, 
        TODAY() >= 
        CASE(MOD(DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8) - DATE(1900,1,7),7), 
        0, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8), 
        1, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+6, 
        2, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+5, 
        3, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+4, 
        4, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+3, 
        5, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+2, 
        DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+1), 
        TODAY() <
        CASE(MOD(DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1) - DATE(1900,1,7),7), 
        0, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1), 
        1, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+6, 
        2, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+5, 
        3, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+4, 
        4, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+3, 
        5, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+2, 
        DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+1)),
    /* CALCULATE FOR IT BEING CURRENTLY DST */
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 6, 2 ) & "/" &
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 9, 2 ) & "/" &
    LEFT( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 4 ) & " " &
    TEXT(
      IF(
        OR(
          VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) = 0,
          VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) = 12), 
            12,
            VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) )
            -
            IF(
              VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) < 12, 0, 12
            )
      )
    )
    &":"&
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 15, 2 )
    &" "&
    IF(
    VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) < 12,
    "AM",
    "PM"
    ),
    /* CALCULATE FOR IT NOT BEING CURRENTLY DST */
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 6, 2 ) & "/" &
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 9, 2 ) & "/" &
    LEFT( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 4 ) & " " &
    TEXT(
      IF(
        OR(
          VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) = 0,
          VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) = 12), 
            12,
            VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) )
            -
            IF(
              VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) < 12, 0, 12
            )
      )
    )
    &":"&
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 15, 2 )
    &" "&
    IF(
    VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__AddressUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) < 12,
    "AM",
    "PM"
    )
  )
)

fields.calculatedFormula:
IF(ISBLANK(smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c), "Unknown",
  IF (AND( smartystreets__Mailing_Daylight_Savings__c, 
        TODAY() >= 
        CASE(MOD(DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8) - DATE(1900,1,7),7), 
        0, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8), 
        1, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+6, 
        2, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+5, 
        3, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+4, 
        4, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+3, 
        5, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+2, 
        DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),3,8)+1), 
        TODAY() <
        CASE(MOD(DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1) - DATE(1900,1,7),7), 
        0, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1), 
        1, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+6, 
        2, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+5, 
        3, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+4, 
        4, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+3, 
        5, DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+2, 
        DATE(YEAR(TODAY()),11,1)+1)),
    /* CALCULATE FOR IT BEING CURRENTLY DST */
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 6, 2 ) & "/" &
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 9, 2 ) & "/" &
    LEFT( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 4 ) & " " &
    TEXT(
      IF(
        OR(
          VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) = 0,
          VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) = 12), 
            12,
            VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) )
            -
            IF(
              VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) < 12, 0, 12
            )
      )
    )
    &":"&
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 15, 2 )
    &" "&
    IF(
    VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ (smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c+1) /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) < 12,
    "AM",
    "PM"
    ),
    /* CALCULATE FOR IT NOT BEING CURRENTLY DST */
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 6, 2 ) & "/" &
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 9, 2 ) & "/" &
    LEFT( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 4 ) & " " &
    TEXT(
      IF(
        OR(
          VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) = 0,
          VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) = 12), 
            12,
            VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) )
            -
            IF(
              VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) < 12, 0, 12
            )
      )
    )
    &":"&
    MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 15, 2 )
    &" "&
    IF(
    VALUE( MID( TEXT( NOW()+ smartystreets__MailingUTCOffset__c /24 ), 12, 2 ) ) < 12,
    "AM",
    "PM"
    )
  )
)
